   JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('osi-cards-logs') || '[]');
   ```

   **App logs:**

   ```javascript
   // In browser console:
   JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('osi-cards-app-logs') || '[]');
   ```

   **Access via services:**
   - `LoggerService.getLogsFromLocalStorage()` - Get library logs
   - `LoggingService.getLogsFromLocalStorage()` - Get app logs

